{"tid":810006,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"做飲食有創意係事半功倍","createTime":"2018-09-07T15:11:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T15:19:35.000Z","uid":205825,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dfe6e74af9573e6ecfcad89d9a35baa8e357356a","tid":810006,"uid":205825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:11:02.000Z","msg":"申：真顧客  非打手<br />\n<br />\n今日董事長拉我去葵涌廣場掃食街<br />\n轉角位有間賣地盤feel 既麻辣小吃店<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/07/224700_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F07%2F224700_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f63c136e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁岩我地兩件都食得辣  睇多2 眼先<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/07/224733_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F07%2F224733_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2d4e2fbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nd 名食哂字改得幾過癮 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/07/225819_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F07%2F225819_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e344d8f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n枱上有個叮叮<br />\n要食好嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   當然要撳鐘仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n你撳佢鐘仔就有招呼<br />\n<br />\n一。 容易同顧客打開話匣子  <br />\n唔洗棟個人企喺度賣笑問人食唔食嘢<br />\n<br />\n二。 未撳鐘仔之前  <br />\n又可以多雙手幫到廚房<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/07/225910_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F07%2F225910_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=613822a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食材用麻辣湯底浸熟再加辣粉<br />\n辣度如圖示<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/07/230058_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F07%2F230058_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=96341d93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n職員同我講笑話試過有客人一埋呢就話「齋條初生BB』唔識廣東話唔會明箇中笑點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇落好狠辣  食落冇想像中死辣湯底ok喎<br />\n<br />\n愛情不也是   有好多次  <br />\n我哋都曾經以為好難過  好痛苦吧呢一關<br />\n<br />\n一口吞咗佢之後先發現 <br />\n其實冇想像中咁難過<br />\n<br />\n食物中讓我悟出一 d 想法<br />\n店員又好傾好笑  <br />\n值得我坐低慢慢寫呢段文字<br />\n<br />\n( 冇鋪號，頂層，食肆區 )<br />\n#麻辣真漢子"},{"pid":"ffa8e689a197f7a9660d7c5b87a4a6cf01856722","tid":810006,"uid":124824,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:12:07.000Z","msg":"打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e31ab8dc2a78cd82aa0def0cf3b390928d67879","tid":810006,"uid":122264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:12:55.000Z","msg":"周星星打手"},{"pid":"e047dea9a5fa3dc29bea4daa206aa80528555607","tid":810006,"uid":205825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffa8e689a197f7a9660d7c5b87a4a6cf01856722","tid":810006,"uid":124824,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:12:07.000Z","msg":"打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:17:39.000Z","msg":"初戀情侶套餐顧客<br />\n籌號120"},{"pid":"2b3327c60a15e1a1cf2bf8c123b12ad6c1b7503c","tid":810006,"uid":205825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e31ab8dc2a78cd82aa0def0cf3b390928d67879","tid":810006,"uid":122264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:12:55.000Z","msg":"周星星打手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:19:35.000Z","msg":"係會令到經過既顧客有聯想既"}]}